    q: "What areas does Vantage Sport & Surface serve?",
    a: "We serve the Northwest Washington region, including Whatcom County (Bellingham, Lynden, Ferndale), Skagit County (Mount Vernon, Anacortes, Burlington), Snohomish County, Island County (Oak Harbor), and the San Juan Islands. Our studio is based in Lynden, WA.",
